Looks like there's 4 single stall rooms each for men and women all inside an air conditioned building.

Nederlands: via de leerlingen ingang door de kleine aula naar het f gebouw en dan naar rechts en via de hoofd ingang door de grote aula en het trappenhuis naar de kleine aula en dan het f gebouw in en dan rechts ergens.

English: through the student entrance youll enter the small "aula" (place students can sit during their break) and proceed to the f building which you can get to through two glass doors and then if you walk a bit it will be to ur right. from the main entrance you have to walk through the big "aula" through the stairwell and via the small "aula" you can get to the f building as described before.
